  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00149:cd53c8f4ea9c]]\n中文写作高频候选短语前十为：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00150:0f2d65da9e82]] 7.36%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00151:bde69029f2bc]] 4.67%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00152:3178cc1c0ec0]] 4.09%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00153:b2fe5a2c3a64]] 3.90%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00154:75b93dc4026a]] 3.60%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00155:cf82bfbe2c75]] 3.47%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00156:0b450da3a431]] 3.39%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00157:296b034a4e8a]] 3.36%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00158:66d41b1df9ba]] 2.74%、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00159:cef4c4920d5b]] 2.57%。",
  "read_only_context_before": "文档画像进一步按路径功能分层：Codex 技能文档 4,823 份、D 盘其他 MD 1,007 份、第三方依赖 924 份、项目文档 367 份、本地报告 176 份。来源类型用于解释写法差异，而不是用于猜测作者身份。",
